<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Sending an array with typed objects, which contain typed objects themselves causes an "Unknows Definition reference" in Zend_Amf_Parse_Amf3_Deserializer (line 304).</p>

<p>Tracing that error back to Zend_Amf_Parse_Amf0_Deserializer i found that the deserializer is created newly everytime readAmf3TypeMarker is called (line 297).</p>

<p>Changing this behaviour back (caching the amf3-parser and using a getter for it) this issue is resolved.</p>

<p>The working Zend_Amf_Parse_Amf0_Deserializer i took was from june 2009 - zendfw 1.8</p>

